item.description:
Alliançe Française d'Hartford is partnering with the West Hartford Art League in an exhibit of John Rohatsch's photographs of Paris. Meet the artist with a reception afterward.
The Art League is in a beautiful, park-like setting. If you have never been there before, you will be pleasantly surprised!
Please note that they request an RSVP at 860-231-8019.

A Photographic Walking Tour of Paris
by John Rohatsch

Sunday September 26, 2010 3 p.m.


Clubhouse Gallery, 37 Buena Vista Road
West Hartford, CT

The West Hartford Art League is pleased to partner with the Alliance Francaise to present a photographic tour of Paris through the eyes of photographer and artist John Rohatsch.

Join us for a reception with the artist,
immediately following the reception.

Free and open to the public.
The presentation will be in English.
Pre-registration appreciated.

Please call the Art League at 860-231-8019
